      <Run Tag="xhtml/part01chapter15.html#page115fn01">Our methodology for comparing players of different eras is based on the &#x201C;Davenport Translations.&#x201D;</Run>
      <Span BaselineAlignment="Superscript" FontFamily="times new roman" FontSize="11">
        <Hyperlink NavigateUri="xhtml/part01chapter15.html#fn01page115">
